#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""cc-scan — Test all Claude models across all providers with a beautiful matrix table.

Loads credentials from:
  - ~/.config/claude-code/direct.env (ANTHROPIC_API_KEY)
  - ~/.config/claude-code/foundry.env (AZURE_FOUNDRY_ENDPOINT, AZURE_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY)
  - ~/.aws/credentials (aws_access_key_id, aws_secret_access_key)
  - ~/.config/cloud-chat-assistant/config.json (fallback for all platforms)
  - gcloud auth print-access-token (Vertex AI)

Tests all 5 model tiers × 5 providers = 25 checks in parallel.
"""

